uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data.stream

Class ByteArrayStreamData

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data.stream.ByteArrayStreamData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, StreamData
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ByteArrayMimeStreamData

    public class ByteArrayStreamData
extends java.lang.Object
implements StreamData, java.io.Externalizable
    Implements StreamData holding the data locally in memory. The Object starts empty and setDataStream must be used to initialise the contents.
